verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Take my hands and let them move,
At the impulse of Thy love;
Take my feet and let them be
Swift and beautiful for Thee.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Take my voice, and let me sing
Always, only, for my King;
Take my lips, and let them be
Filled with messages from Thee.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Take my silver and my gold;
Not a mite would I withold;
Take my intellect, and use
Every power as You choose.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Take my will, and make it Thine;
It shall be no longer mine.
Take my heart; it is Thine own;
It shall be Thy royal throne.{/lang-eng}
